#: src/development/testing.md:459
msgid ""
"The Dockerfile builds three per-source leaf stages — `pyenv-test`, `conda-"
"test`, `venvwrapper-test` — on top of a shared `scoop-test-base`. Each "
"carries only the source-tool it migrates from, so CI can matrix-build just "
"one variant."
